About :: GG_Office_Mini2
Hello World
This map is a remake of my old map ( gg_office_mini ) as the maps was decent attempt at mapping I decided to make a remake. More optimized, better game play, and what all the GG players want these days. I really focused on optimizing working with hint/skip textures for the first time. I learned a lot on optimazing and optimzed this map from 120fps to 200+ fps, Once you learn it's very easy.

The map has a basic style as the original map cs_office. This gg map is like a stipend version of it. Interms of gameplay i tested on a sample gg server with 24players and it was fun. Try it out your self.

Hope you like it.


-Cezaris LT

General Info
Map Name: gg_office_mini2

Frequently Asked Questions
Can I decompile this map for learning purposes?
- Yes you can. I will allow this just for learning purposes. Please do not copy parts of my map. Here is the VTF file.

Can I copy parts and add it to my map?
- Not with out my permission. You can go ahead and ask me first and I may allow this.

Can I distribute you'r map?
- As long as you keep my name there, Yes.

I have a shitty pc, will this run?
- Yes, It's very optimized. I have a decent pc and I get around 200fps so most of the people should have no problems.

How can I make the cool colord boxes you made above?
- Learn CSS then go here.
